					<img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/deb3b6f1bd3c1a7cbd48b35455b44212?s=80&amp;d=&amp;r=PG' class='avatar avatar-80 photo' height='80' width='80' />					<cite class="fn"><a href='http://www.lisabelle-artist.com' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Lisa_Belle</a></cite>				</div><!-- .comment-author .vcard -->
				
				<div class="comment-meta commentmetadata">
					<a href="http://cerebralrift.org/2014/05/06/the-fda-admits-it-is-over-reaching/#comment-18289"><time datetime="2014-05-12T18:24:40+00:00">
